de.feig.TagHandler
Class FedmIscTagHandler_ISO14443_4_MIFARE_DESFire_FlexSoftCrypto

java.lang.Object
  de.feig.TagHandler.FedmIscTagHandler_ISO14443_4_MIFARE_DESFire_FlexSoftCrypto

public class FedmIscTagHandler_ISO14443_4_MIFARE_DESFire_FlexSoftCrypto
extends java.lang.Object

Class for ISO 14443-4 transponder Infineon MIFARE DESFire using the [0xC3] Flexible Software Cryptography.
This class supports only selected mode in Host-Mode.
